  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic package carries a W-CON-01 weakener: the decision record records outcome Accepted while several credibility factors omit both requiredLevel and achievedLevel, leaving the acceptance decision unsupported by structured factor evidence.",
